      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! It has some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it remains a solid performer that drives well and offers great value. It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point!",
