    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The engine runs roughly and exhibits several noticeable fluid leaks that need immediate professional inspection. Externally, the body shows signs of neglect, including visible rust patches, several dents, and faded paint. The interior is also heavily worn, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a restoration project or for parts.",
