    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and well-presented car. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor, typical road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a faint scratch near the trunk lid. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin is clean and has been well-preserved; the upholstery shows no tears or stains, though there is some light softening of the leather on the driver\u2019s seat bolster.",
